{"tid":1975269,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(香港悲哀）【曾聲演野原廣志】「小新老竇」癌症病逝 終年55歲","createTime":"2020-04-16T12:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T14:00:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f8d02149b6c0105b968d88cb9349f675292b94","tid":1975269,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200416/large/1587022710_49c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1587022710_49c3.jpg&h=ed46e8af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在《蠟筆小新》中聲演小新老竇野原廣志的聲優藤原啓治於本月12日逝世，終年55歲，他負責擔任社長的AIR AGENCY今日在官網公佈死訊。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指：「本公司的社長兼所屬聲優藤原啓因為癌症，於令和2年4月12日病逝。」網站又指守夜和告別式只招待親人出席。藤原於1964年10月5日在東京出生，除了動畫外，亦曾為不少外國電影及劇集做配音工作，由青年到老年的角色都有，代表作是《蠟筆小新》的野原廣志，還在《鋼之鍊金術師》、《HUNTER&times;HUNTER》等演出，他亦在日本版《復仇者聯盟》（The Avengers）中聲演鐵甲奇俠。"},{"pid":"649858593380c300a4a6cbdc7c76c365c37eca08","tid":1975269,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200416/VMXA2UJO5VCJKREVIYPQ6NFZQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200416%2FVMXA2UJO5VCJKREVIYPQ6NFZQA%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10LyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=7210678b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200416%2FVMXA2UJO5VCJKREVIYPQ6NFZQA%2F&h=94839e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200416/VMXA2UJO5VCJKREVIYPQ6NFZQA/</a>"},{"pid":"fffe2d918d662e2d1c43b3fe9a08c32fa3fdf080","tid":1975269,"uid":309015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9e4a996ebb4bcb05c53ac5cb966c2be3b05b35","tid":1975269,"uid":